I"¶<p> Salarpuria Greenage is a residential complex on Hosur Road in Bengaluru. We are a short distance away from Koramangala and HSR Layout. The complex is located next to Oxford College and also an upcoming metro station on RV Road - Bommasandra 'Yellow line'. 
  
We are a community of 1676 flats, grouped into 10 Towers/Blocks. About 70% of the total area is open spaces with a lot of walking paths, sitting areas and green cover. 
